---
title: 21 Day Aged Sirloin Steak and Garlic Thyme Butter with Peri Peri Chips and Mint & Chilli Peas
description: Our 21 Day Aged Sirloin Steak and Garlic Thyme Butter combines premium beef with delicious sides to bring the steakhouse to your table.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R32_W13_UK_SSN11274-3_Main_high-7bae0c3e.jpg
